#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:89
msgid ""
"Payloads are encrypted at rest. You control where data lives: run Password Pus"
"her on your own servers, in your cloud, or in Docker. Thousands of companies a"
"nd teams self-host it so sensitive data never touches third-party SaaS."
msgstr ""
"Nyttelaster krypteres i hviletilstand. Du styrer, hvor dataene befinder sig: K"
"ør Password Pusher på dine egne servere, i din cloud eller i Docker. Tusindvis"
" af virksomheder og teams hoster det selv, så følsomme data aldrig rører tredj"
"eparts SaaS."

#: ../../../app/views/pages/about.html.erb:92
msgid ""
"No account is required for basic use; optional user accounts and sign-in let t"
"eams track their own pushes. The source code is open so you can review and ada"
"pt it."
msgstr ""
"Der kræves ingen konto til grundlæggende brug; valgfrie brugerkonti og login g"
"iver teams mulighed for at spore deres egne pushes. Kildekoden er åben, så du "
"kan gennemgå og tilpasse den."

